title: ArchiveMac 1.1.3 [K].zip
description:
ArchiveMac is an application for Mac OS X Leopard which supports archiving large files to CD, DVD, or Blu-Ray. It can split large files and directories so that they span multiple discs. When restoring, the original file or directory is restored regardless of how large it is. There is no file or directory size limit.

WHAT'S NEW
Version 1.1.3: Fixed bug causing error when burning large number of files to a DVD.

REQUIREMENTS
Mac OS X 10.5 or later. CD, DVD or Blu-ray burner.
